OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776618353
OL,3,CAround 414,000 hit in school cyber
OL,4,Cattack as system 'largely restored'
OL,6,FAn IT system for Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fschools has been "largely restored"
OL,8,Ffollowing a cyber attack, the
OL,9,FEducation Authority has said.
OL,11,FThe C2k system was targeted in the
OL,12,Fattack earlier this month.
OL,14,FOn Thursday a 16-year-old boy was
OL,15,Farrested by detectives investigating
OL,16,Fthe incident.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@cO]
