OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776618353
OL,3,CAround 414,000 hit in school cyber
OL,4,Cattack as system 'largely restored'
OL,6,FOn Friday the Education Authority (EA)
OL,7,Fsaid more than 414,000 user accounts,
OL,8,Fincluding pupils, teachers and non-
OL,9,Fteaching staff, have been successfully
OL,10,Freconnected, bringing the system "back
OL,11,Fto close to normal levels of
OL,12,Foperation".
OL,14,FIt said the number of calls to the C2k
OL,15,Fservice desk have now "significantly
OL,16,Freduced and is now in line with a
OL,17,Ftypical school day".
OL,19,FIt also said the majority of systems
OL,20,Fand services schools need to access
OL,21,Fare also now available.
OL,26,@rD@bOUtD@JO]wD@WOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
