PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776618353
OL,3,CAround 414,000 hit in school cyber
OL,4,Cattack as system 'largely restored'
OL,6,F"We would like to thank schools, staff
OL,7,Facross the EA, partners, and our
OL,8,Fservice provider for their significant
OL,9,Fefforts and commitment throughout this
OL,10,Fperiod," a EA spokesperson said in a
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,F"We are also very grateful to parents/
OL,14,Fcarers, pupils and school communities
OL,15,Ffor their patience and cooperation
OL,16,Fthroughout this challenging period.
OL,18,F"The EA is continuing to work closely
OL,19,Fwith a small number of schools that
OL,20,Fwere specifically targeted, where some
OL,21,Fpersonal data was compromised.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]uD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
