OL,3,CAround 414,000 hit in school cyber
OL,4,Cattack as system 'largely restored'
OL,6,F"We will be contacting any impacted
OL,7,Findividuals directly to provide
OL,8,Ffurther information, advice and
OL,9,Fguidance.
OL,11,F"They do not need to take any further
OL,12,Faction at this stage."
